The '''''Throat Slasher''''' was the personal [[Starship/Legends|starship]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Hunters|hunter]] [[Tsaa Qalu]].

It was small enough to be flown by a single [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]], and highly maneuverable, but also large enough to carry two [[Yorik-et|coralskippers]]. Aft of the flight [[Bridge (starship)/Legends|bridge]] lay a corridor with access to another chamber, and [[Airlock/Legends|airlock]], beyond which lay the fighter docks and a hold that could be used to carry [[Prisoner/Legends|prisoners]]. A second [[Warrior caste|warrior]], [[Laph Rapuung]], served as pilot, and perhaps the only other crew member.

In [[27 ABY/Legends|27 ABY]], the ''Throat Slasher'' was used to track the ''[[No Luck Required]]'' from [[Wayland/Legends|Wayland]] to [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]], but it was destroyed when the [[Dug/Legends|Dug]] prisoner [[Leaft]] escaped and stole one of the coralskippers, forcing the ship to crash into a mountainside.

